00:43.080 --> 00:45.059
(Laughter and playful chatter)

00:46.800 --> 00:49.621
DEMELZ4:
Dearest
R055,
you are safely missed

00:49.800 --> 00:51.461
by your ch/Yo'ren, your wife,

00:51.640 --> 00:52.959
your 0'09"-

00:53.120 --> 00:55.259
and by a// at home for whom you speak.

00:55.440 --> 00:57.305
